<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<sample sampleID="LBf9_00132" version="1.0" type="fixedLength">
<article articleID="LBf9_00132_F001">
<paragraph>
<sentence>昔は、どっちかといえば、芳恵の方がいつも年下の典子に付き合ってあ<sampling type="start" />げているという感じだったのだが。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「―何かあったの」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>と、典子は言った。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「え？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「ぼんやりしてるし…。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">いつもより疲れてるみたいよ」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「ごめんなさい。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">ゆうべ、ちょっとよく眠れなかったの」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>と芳恵は目を伏せた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「そう。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">色々大変でしょうね、ご主人がいないと」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　芳恵は答えなかった。</sentence>
<sentence>―熱いスープが出て来て、ゆっくりと口へ流し込むと、少し気持が<ruby rubyText="なご">和</ruby>んで来た。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「―私ね」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence type="quasi">と、典子が<ruby rubyText="とう">唐</ruby><ruby rubyText="とつ">突</ruby>に、<quote>「あの毛皮店の男の人と、時々会ってるのよ」</quote></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「向いのお店の？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「そう。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">なかなかすてきでしょ」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「そうね。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">会ってるって…」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「帰りの早い時とかね。</sentence>
<sentence>彼は家族持ちだから、そうゆっくりできないけど、ホテルで一時間ぐらい…。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">私が眠ってる間に、彼は帰ってるわ」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　典子のあっけらかんとした言い方に、芳恵は<ruby rubyText="めん">面</ruby><ruby rubyText="く">食</ruby>らってしまった。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「じゃ…。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">不倫ってことね」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　典子は笑い出して、</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「あなたが言うと、三十年も昔の言葉みたいね」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>と、ナプキンで口を<ruby rubyText="ぬぐ">拭</ruby>った。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi"><quote><sentence>「私だって、佐原でこりてるから、のめり込まないようにしてるわ。</sentence>
<sentence>向うも遊びと割り切って。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">―結構いいもんよ」</sentence>
</quote></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「お楽しみね」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>と、芳恵は笑って言った。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「あなた、どう？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「どう、って…」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「一度、よかったら彼とデートしてみない？</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">　お貸しするわ」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「あら」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　芳恵はびっくりした。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi"><quote><sentence>「まさか！</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">　そんなことできないわ」</sentence>
</quote></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「いいじゃない。</sentence>
<sentence>ホテルへ行くのが、気が<ruby rubyText="とが">咎</ruby>めるなら、おしゃべりするだけでも。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">気が晴れるわよ」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「気をつかってくれるのね」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「夫のいない<ruby rubyText="さび">寂</ruby>しさって、身にしみてるからよ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>と、典子は真顔で言った。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi"><quote><sentence>「息抜きの恋だって、それで元気になって、うんと働ければ結構なことじゃない。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">ご主人には分りっこないわよ」</sentence>
</quote></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「そんな―そんなこと、できないわ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>と、芳恵は首を振った。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi"><quote><sentence>「私…。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">ふさいでるのは、そんなことじゃないの」</sentence>
</quote></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「じゃ、何？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　芳恵は少しためらって、</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「昨夜、佐原が来たのよ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「まあ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「夜中の二時ごろかしら。</sentence>
<sentence>―ドアをノックするから、<ruby rubyText="だれ">誰</ruby>かと思ったら…。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">もちろん、中には入れなかったわ」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「そうよ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">あんなの、のたれ死にでも、すりゃいいんだわ」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「帰って下さい、って、ドア越しに言ってやったんだけど、しつこくて…。</sentence>
<sentence>結局、中には入れなかったけど、三時過ぎまで、うろうろしてたんじゃないかしら。</sentence>
<sentence>その後も、気になって眠れなかったの。</sentence>
<sentence>―それで今日はボーッとしてて。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">ごめんなさい」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「そんなこと、いいのよ。</sentence>
<sentence>佐原、何か言ってた？」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「いいえ。</sentence>
<sentence>ただ『行くところがなくて』とか『今夜だけ泊めて下さい』とか…。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">哀れっぽい声を出してたわ」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　典子は苦笑して、</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「プレイボーイ台なしね。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">そんな男に夢中になってたかと思うと、我ながら情ない」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「もうよしましょう、佐原の話は」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence type="quasi">と、芳恵は言って、運ばれて来たランチの皿を見て、<quote>「<sentence>わあ、おいしそう！」</sentence>
</quote></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence>と、声を上げた…。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<blockEnd />
<paragraph>
<sentence>　―ランチを終えて店に戻ると、典子は、すぐに向いの毛皮店へ行って、十五分ほどして戻って来た。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「ね、芳恵さん」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「何？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「今日は早く帰らなきゃまずいの？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「特別には…。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">で<sampling type="end" />も守が帰るまでには、何とか―」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
</article>
</sample>
